  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/338b6cd3fb7012ae6bca4b42d553167e.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alma's in a tight spot -- she's a magical researcher, but has no funds for her research! She's got no choice but to head to the tavern and take on a commission... but the one she ends up with is suspiciously short on details.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enticed by the reward money, she sets out to meet the mysterious client...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/5ecbf66a8af82164d88b3a91b503f4c3.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/04bec5761bcfded7d3ac50af98c3b783.poster.avif?t=1759193652\" width=400 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/04bec5761bcfded7d3ac50af98c3b783.webm?t=1759193652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/04bec5761bcfded7d3ac50af98c3b783.mp4?t=1759193652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a traditional, turn-based RPG. Since Alma is a mage, you'll be using magic to blast your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After you beat the game, you can start again with all the levels, money, and spells you acquired the first time around!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your TP hits 100 during battle, you can unleash a Magical Boost (M-Boost)!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alma's magic power, evasion, and accuracy will go into overdrive, and she'll be able to use special spells for the duration! However, MP cost for spells is increased by 50%!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose just the right time for an M-Boost, and even the most fearsome foes don't stand a chance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/de0e2dbd20ffc6fd32ef57ba7823e440.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/b71ca42736416143742d283fcfe2a567.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/21ce058e0ff53922af493f8c44cbeb9d.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/7bfd633bb95d274ed1d30d11d88bdd4b.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/338b6cd3fb7012ae6bca4b42d553167e.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alma's in a tight spot -- she's a magical researcher, but has no funds for her research! She's got no choice but to head to the tavern and take on a commission... but the one she ends up with is suspiciously short on details.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enticed by the reward money, she sets out to meet the mysterious client...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/5ecbf66a8af82164d88b3a91b503f4c3.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/04bec5761bcfded7d3ac50af98c3b783.poster.avif?t=1759193652\" width=400 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/04bec5761bcfded7d3ac50af98c3b783.webm?t=1759193652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/04bec5761bcfded7d3ac50af98c3b783.mp4?t=1759193652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a traditional, turn-based RPG. Since Alma is a mage, you'll be using magic to blast your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After you beat the game, you can start again with all the levels, money, and spells you acquired the first time around!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your TP hits 100 during battle, you can unleash a Magical Boost (M-Boost)!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alma's magic power, evasion, and accuracy will go into overdrive, and she'll be able to use special spells for the duration! However, MP cost for spells is increased by 50%!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose just the right time for an M-Boost, and even the most fearsome foes don't stand a chance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/de0e2dbd20ffc6fd32ef57ba7823e440.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/b71ca42736416143742d283fcfe2a567.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/21ce058e0ff53922af493f8c44cbeb9d.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338550/extras/7bfd633bb95d274ed1d30d11d88bdd4b.avif?t=1759193652\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p>",
